Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重申一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次作战 以歌姬号为旗舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽坐镇舰桥指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还须歌姬号舰长协助司令部运转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蕾丝中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近处看上去还真俊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 各舰来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰队 开始出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您果然要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前线更易作出精确指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这场战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要返回火星圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内人不曾冰眠 时光蹉跎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共度最后的时光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们告诉我作战部署
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是预备队？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不安排我去最前线？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 德西尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保后备兵源是战术之本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防万一 命令你待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对菲利特·明日野 你有特殊的感情在作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样上战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么错！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要干掉菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 我活到今天的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再放任他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何做？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会考虑处分的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现敌人舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 是击退那些人类公敌的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰 开始布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子环形阵列 准备启动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为电磁终端输入坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我军最新武器 光子环形阵列是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是将电磁终端呈圆环状排列在宇宙空间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令电子在内侧旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造出强大的动能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用歌姬号的光子爆破炮完成指向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 如何不被敌人察觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子环充电完成前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得让敌人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我们要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为此需要做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗到最后的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论对手是谁 都要战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗虽苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是失去战友会更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住了吗 要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…刚才谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 一定活着要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不合时宜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次…关于求婚的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如…如果不嫌弃我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发咯 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野
