Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 巴雷特双枪的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上次那个X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 这高达不是菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不腻味也难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二战队 追击敌机动战士队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游击部队投入作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怪阵是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使我方集中兵力 引诱我们中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩挲副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让达乌内斯紧急调头 朝向坐标F21方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 机动战士队正准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令他们停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推进系统应急模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军已经完成了那个东西
