Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止追击敌人 立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 好不容易突破阵线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子环形阵列
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放射环确认形成
