Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人似乎部署了某种干涉掩体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
