Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体…不听使唤…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙我对付得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等阿莉莎她们
