Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 亚瑟姆
