Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号…消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 沃尔夫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有人从我的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 迄今为止多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提多尽兴了
