Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你 绝不放过
